# Dedicated speedtest backend. Defaults to the production Hostinger backend
# (https://speed.netspeed.me); set this only to point at a staging or local
# instance (see https://github.com/josephjo31/netspeed-backend). The server
# must expose CORS-enabled endpoints:
#   GET  /ping                 -> JSON latency probe
#   GET  /download?size=100MB  -> streams incompressible bytes
#   POST /upload               -> accepts and discards a binary body
# NOTE: NEXT_PUBLIC_* vars are inlined at build time — rebuild after changing.
NEXT_PUBLIC_TEST_SERVER_URL=
